
= Tchepédia.rs is a collaborative encyclopedia about the "Gaúcho" culture.

URL = http://tchepedia.rs


=Description=

Tchêpédia   allows people to enter typical words and phrases of the "Gaúcho"   culture in a digital encyclopedia, which works collaboratively,  allowing  users to not only register with the terms, but also edit and  comment on  everything that is added to the site.


